                    ADVYSER - ENGINEERING PLAN
                    Auth Flow Restoration + Contact Details Gate
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Date:    2026-02-25
Status:  APPROVED - READY TO IMPLEMENT
Branch:  main
Backup:  codex/non-public-backup-20260211


ğŸ“‹ Context
â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€

Auth pages (login, signup, verify, forgot-password, auth/callback) were deleted in Phase 8
as part of a "public-only MVP" prune. They exist in full working condition on the backup
branch. The intended MVP requires users to sign up before seeing advisor contact details.
Currently, contact details are fully public and no auth UI exists on the site.

This plan restores the auth flow and wires the contact details paywall.


