In the success state (~lines 350-357), add "Complete your profile" CTA above the
existing action buttons. The email is already captured in formData.email (Step 2).

New CTA block to add BEFORE the existing button row:

  <div className="rounded-lg border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 p-6 mb-8 text-center space-y-3">
    <p className="font-semibold text-foreground">One more step - secure your account</p>
    <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      Complete your profile to track your request and hear back from advisors.
    </p>
    <Button className="w-full sm:w-auto" asChild>
      <Link href={`/signup?email=${encodeURIComponent(formData.email || "")}&redirect=/`}>
        Complete your profile
      </Link>
    </Button>
  </div>

Demote existing buttons to variant="outline" and variant="ghost".


